### 健康检查 - 二维码
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/qrcode/health

### 健康检查 - 验证
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/validate/health


### 生成二维码
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/qrcode/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "https://www.example.com",
  "size": 300,
  "format": "PNG"
}

### 验证邮箱
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/validate/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gmail.com",
  "checkMx": true,
  "checkDisposable": true
}

### 验证电话号码 - 美国
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/validate/phone
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "+1-202-555-0173",
  "countryCode": "US"
}

### 验证电话号码 - 中国
